PFMonitor is a cutting edge system for Remotely Managing all of your
pfSense & OPNSense Firewalls, seeing live threat analytics of hits to
your devices, Tracking Failed Logins, Managing reboots with a single
click, And even Pushing Firmware Upgrades without having to even log
into the pfSense or OPNSense units.

WWW: https://pfmonitor.com
